{"tid":2260112,"cid":37,"subCid":13,"title":"究竟係師傅問題定我地問題","createTime":"2020-10-27T10:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T01:09:43.000Z","uid":120746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"33a9a333c84d5caac9ab921fe5e394095a706611","tid":2260112,"uid":120746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T10:35:44.000Z","msg":"想請教一下究竟圖中灰色地磚本身隻掃口粉係咩色？<br />\n覺得師傅用咗黃色 裝修完都好似冇裝修過咁 又舊又黃<br />\n但佢又堅持係用咗白色<br />\n於是叫佢嚟執修 佢掃完白色後更加顯得本身果隻掃口粉係黃 <br />\n（圖中係掃完白色掃口粉 已經極速甩色 所以一達達咁）<br />\n第三張圖係對比返廳用嘅黃色 直頭係一樣色啦？<br />\n但佢都係堅持話用咗白色 <br />\n又話可能果陣裝修地下吸左啲唔知咩料之 搞到變左唔白<br />\n<br />\n有無人可以俾啲意見？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KPdNY7S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKPdNY7S.jpg&h=2927de97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0jQWUQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0jQWUQ.jpg&h=94556f83&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wsEEQeR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwsEEQeR.jpg&h=85dc157c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"959cd9cfce647abdc1d53de6972941c537021838","tid":2260112,"uid":16685,"like":18,"dislike":15,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T10:41:59.000Z","msg":"掃口都咁撚多要求，過幾個月都變黑嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6a015361477f0091aea9c374a117a1e0061791","tid":2260112,"uid":185631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"959cd9cfce647abdc1d53de6972941c537021838","tid":2260112,"uid":16685,"like":18,"dislike":15,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T10:41:59.000Z","msg":"掃口都咁撚多要求，過幾個月都變黑嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T10:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f59cff65692e18984996386336d53c